{"tid":414153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喺連登屌連狗就多正評, 屌林狗就多負評","createTime":"2017-09-26T04:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T10:05:51.000Z","uid":52023,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ab73e231379ccfcc462ff2c441257be0f696edf6","tid":414153,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T04:00:06.000Z","msg":"喺高登講連狗?講lihkg?post 都俾人del撚埋喇<br />\n<br />\n林狗條中坑又樣衰又冇料到又脫節又虛偽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n估唔到都喺呢邊都養養埋埋咁多奶閪fans <br />\n成晚喺度回家回巢 仲肉鳩酸過TVB<br />\n<br />\n之前高登仔仲笑鳩台仔鍾意推啲冇料人士上位造神<br />\n實情嗰班&quot;自稱&quot;所謂&quot;高質啲&quot;嘅高登仔一樣是非不分<br />\n狗屎垃圾都吹奏一餐"},{"pid":"b5079983bcbcdf7369408dc44e50dd61a5fbdcb2","tid":414153,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T04:03:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6bebe0cadc9431de8bf8bf5fda7510098b53106","tid":414153,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T04:05:32.000Z","msg":"呢度得返班新會員<br />\n撚知林祖舜做埋d仆街野咩"},{"pid":"c2e9e58c0c0aafdbee02917b5b807775583daa67","tid":414153,"uid":52023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T04:10:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢度得返班新會員<br />\n撚知林祖舜做埋d仆街野咩</blockquote><br />\n呢條撚樣當初LIHKG開壇都未識死<br />\n喺度牙斬斬笑騎騎<br />\n當年冇HKG+班高登仔仲喺度熄緊燈喳 上撚到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呀JOE當年仲瀨鳩人哋個APP拎佢料拎到死SER<br />\n當初你個官方即使手機版好少少都唔會俾HKG+發到圍啦"},{"pid":"a5f1a6eedb0dd7a8fedf7960e98f551351743c01","tid":414153,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T04:36:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a15dc4ba5ed134732c82974fe3621c8c1b229eab","tid":414153,"uid":49992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T04:38:33.000Z","msg":"叫人返高登都冇俾人del po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日係開po叫人返高登<img